snippet.title: Space Marshals - New Update! Chapter Three!
snippet.description:
The third and concluding chapter in the Space Marshals saga is upon us! This trailer shows some of the new weapons, levels, enemies and evil bosses you'll face in this massive update. Available August 13.

Please subscribe to get updates on the latest games and updates. Cheers!
